        <title>Mathematical Practice 2 as a Learner</title>
        <contents>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;To investigate MP&amp;nbsp;2 further, we’ll now look at some student work on the task Best Buy Tickets from the &lt;a href="https://www.map.mathshell.org/background.php" target="_blank" title="Mathematics Assessment Project website - opens in a new window"&gt;Mathematics Assessment Project&lt;/a&gt;    of the Mathematics Assessment Resource Service (CCRS Mathematics: A.CED.1, MP.4).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;First, do the task yourself (see the handout &lt;a href="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Best%20Buy%20Tickets.pdf?time=1688697555777" target="_blank" title="PDF - opens in a new window"&gt;Best Buy Tickets&lt;/a&gt;). You won’t have to submit your solution,
    but it will be handy to have your work available during the rest of the activity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;Once you have completed the task, click NEXT to continue.&lt;/p&gt;</contents>
